data.description: Welcome HOME!!! WITH ZERO LOT FEES, AND YOU OWN your LAND!  Brookhaven Village is A very welcoming 55 plus community with shuffleboard, a beautiful community clubhouse and a HEATED POOL all at your disposal!!! This unit is immaculately well kept! This two bedroom and two bathroom unit provides tons of natural light and a very open floorplan. Nice laminate flooring in main living area, Florida room that is screened in, Roof was replaced six years ago with commercial grade materials, AC is 6-7 years old. Washer and dryer are in the shed in the carport, units are one year old. Tons of storage in the home and bigger master bedroom. Schedule your showing today. Seller is willing to assist with closing cost and prepaids. Come see this home for yourself!!!
